#### SMART POINTERS ####

Add <memory> header for smart pointers 

## shared_ptr ##

Specs
    sharedptr.reset(new Entity) -> reset function is replaces the managed object
    std::shared_ptr is a smart pointer that retains shared ownership of an object through a pointer
    sharedptr.get() -> return referance
    make_shared -> creates a shared pointer that manages a new object
    
thread usage;
    need -pthread to makefile otherwise we can get core dump error




